<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Client Reservation Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
  <div style="height: auto; background: linear-gradient(to top, #cbea7b 50%, #9dc209 90%); width: 400px; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
    <h1 style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">New Reservation Alert!</h1>
    <hr style="border: 1px solid #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <p style="color: #fff;">Dear Nutritionist,</p>
    <p style="color: #fff;">A new client has made a reservation on our platform.</p>
    <p style="color: #fff;"><strong>Client Name:</strong> {{clientName}}</p>
    <p style="color: #fff;"><strong>Date and Time:</strong> {{reservationDate}}</p>
    <br>
    <p style="color: #fff;">Please log in to your dashboard to view more details.</p>
    <a href="http://localhost:4200/login"
       target="_blank"
       style="background: #cc5500; padding: 10px; border: none; color: white; border-radius: 4px; display: block; margin: 0 auto; width: 50%; text-align: center; text-decoration: none;">
      Login
    </a>
    <br>
    <p style="color: #fff;">Kind Regards,<br><br>
    NutriSolutions</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
